    "Condition : 2 - The development hereby permitted shall be carried out in accordance with the following approved plans and documents:\r\nVK-01 01, VK-02 01, VK-03 01, VK-04 01, Site Location Plan, Site Block Plan, Design and Access Statement (23 Feb 2022), Reasonable Exception Statement (Fire Safety)\r\nREASON: For the avoidance of doubt and in the interests of proper planning.\r\n\r\n",
